---
// Legacy URL preserved: /who-we-are/ . Copy improved per locked spec; every
// fact from the harvest kept (10+ years, family business, Alexandra Park
// location, visit-before-booking offer, pain-free/industry-standards
// memberships). Source: grooming-image-archive/who-we-are/copy.md.
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import HillDivider from '../components/HillDivider.astro';
import { business } from '../data/business';
import pricing from '../data/pricing.json';
import salon from '../assets/pages/who-we-are/salon.jpg';
---

<Base
  title="The Fairy Tails Dog Grooming - The Fairy Tails Dog Grooming"
  description="As part of The Fairy Tails K9 Centre, we are the caring Hastings dog groomers and are proud to contribute to the health and wellbeing of thousands of dogs in the local area."
  path="/who-we-are/"
>
  <article data-page="who-we-are">
    <header class="bg-moss-900 pb-16 pt-32 sm:pb-20 sm:pt-40">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4">
        <p class="eyebrow text-honey-300">Who we are</p>
        <h1 class="mt-4 font-display text-4xl font-bold leading-tight text-cream-50 sm:text-5xl">
          The caring Hastings dog groomers
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-4 max-w-xl text-lg text-cream-200">
          Part of The Fairy Tails K9 Centre, with over 10 years' experience of caring for dogs —
          and helping their humans.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>
    <HillDivider class="text-moss-900" flip />

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-6 pt-10 sm:pt-14">
      <div class="grid items-center gap-10 md:grid-cols-2">
        <div>
          <p class="eyebrow text-honey-700">Where you'll find us</p>
          <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-moss-900">
            On the edge of Alexandra Park
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-bark-700">
            The salon sits at the bottom of Mount Pleasant Road, within walking distance of
            Alexandra Park, with outside shop parking should you wish to drop off or collect your
            dog. If you'd rather we came to you, we collect and drop off across {pricing.pickup.areas}
            {' '}for £{pricing.pickup.journeyPrice} a journey on full grooms.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-bark-700">
            Grooming is one part of the full Fairy Tails family: alongside the salon, the
            <a href={business.sisterSite} class="font-bold text-moss-800 underline decoration-honey-500 underline-offset-4">K9 Centre</a>
            {/* Owner ruling 2026-07-16 (evening): day school and day care are BOTH
                real and DIFFERENT things — name both, matching the K9 Centre
                site's own naming ("Dog Day School" is its flagship service;
                daycare is distinct). Logged in WEBSITE-PLAN.md. */}
            offers training, day school and daycare — a complete range of care for your dog.
          </p>
        </div>
        <figure class="polaroid">
          <Image
            src={salon}
            alt="The Fairy Tails premises"
            widths={[480, 800, 1024]}
            sizes="(min-width: 768px) 50vw, 100vw"
            loading="eager"
          />
        </figure>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pt-14">
      <p class="eyebrow text-honey-700">A family business</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-moss-900">Small is beautiful</h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-bark-700">
        We are a small, family-run business specialising in all things dog. Our grooming team is
        at the heart of it — contributing to the health and wellbeing of thousands of dogs in the
        Hastings area. We care for dogs of all shapes and sizes and tailor our care to meet your
        dog's needs.
      </p>

      <p class="eyebrow mt-12 text-honey-700">Our team</p>
      <h2 class="mt-3 font-display text-3xl font-bold text-moss-900">
        Happy staff means happy dogs
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed text-bark-700">
        We are very proud of our qualified and experienced team — all part of The Fairy Tails
        family. Most of the dogs we care for absolutely love our staff, and when you book a groom
        they'll do their very best to make it a happy experience for your dog.
      </p>

      <ul class="mt-8 space-y-2 text-sm text-bark-600">
        <li class="paw-bullet">As members, we are committed to pain-free dog care.</li>
        <li class="paw-bullet">As members, we are committed to improving industry standards.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 pb-24 pt-14 text-center">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-cream-100 px-6 py-12">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-moss-900">Come and visit us</h2>
        <p class="mx-auto mt-4 max-w-md leading-relaxed text-bark-700">
          Don't just take our word for it — we're more than happy for you to visit with your dog
          and discuss their needs in detail before booking a groom.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-7 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
          <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-moss">Arrange a visit</a>
          <a href={business.booking.jotform} class="btn btn-honey">Book Appointment</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </article>
</Base>
